Algorithm


Locked me Algorithm and data structures

1:Prompt user to choose option in add files,delete files,List files and add more files

2:If user enters option 1 ask user to enter the no of the files to add

3:Prompt users to enter files

4:Add all the files 

5:If user enter 2 option then ask the user to enter no of files to delete

6:Delete the entered files

7:if user enter option 3 ask user to display your files

8:if user enter option 4 ask user file to search the file

9:if user enter option 5 to exit from application


 Data structures used are 

1:Map

2:ArrayList

